{"tid":2289280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安心App窺用家相片 檔案  索大量權限 IT專家：不符比例","createTime":"2020-11-17T07:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T07:23:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f5da006400d31605199f87a01d9a8963231be66e","tid":2289280,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:03:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/WLP7MB5BT5HCHBS4OBFSP3VAZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2FWLP7MB5BT5HCHBS4OBFSP3VAZ4%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4zsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=0a1560ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2FWLP7MB5BT5HCHBS4OBFSP3VAZ4%2F&h=058bf0cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/WLP7MB5BT5HCHBS4OBFSP3VAZ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n安心App窺用家相片 檔案 <br />\n索大量權限 IT專家：不符比例<br />\n<br />\n【心慌出行】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：二維碼位置隱蔽 市民冷待<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府昨推出「安心出行」感染風險通知流動應用程式，但當中涉及的私隱問題一直惹人關注，就在流動應用程式推出首天，有網民及資訊科技界人士發現程式的Android版本要求大量權限，包括容許讀取用家手機內相片及媒體內容、檢視網絡連線等。數據科學家黃浩華質疑，為何「安心出行」功能不算多，但卻要求用家交出不成比例的權限，更提醒用戶要留意讀取相片或Wi-Fi權限要求，保障私隱風險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VdjPZkgMWO2jQftyw28_5Et2-IM=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z4X6MXK7BRDQBCLJRJVQVVUA6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVdjPZkgMWO2jQftyw28_5Et2-IM%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ4X6MXK7BRDQBCLJRJVQVVUA6Q.jpg&h=e75d535e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大埔多處貼出「安心出行」App的相關通告及二維碼，但未見有市民駐足掃描。<br />\n<br />\n負責程式開發的創新及科技局局長薛永恒曾多次強調，明白市民重視個人私隱，又指所有出行資料只會存放在用戶手機，不會存於中央資料庫，不過昨有網民拆解「安心出行」應用程式原碼，發現iOS版本的權限要求相對簡單，例如要求開啟相機功能；Android版本則有多項額外要求，包括讀取用家手機的相片、媒體、檔案以及儲存空間、更改或刪除儲存體內容、檢視網絡連線及所有的網絡位置和權限等。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：變種病毒掀第四波 南亞客酒店播疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3nJbm1w9gixiwasx9TxNYH2K6TA=/413x761/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PN7MWKDFPNCVFD3T4YX6UDPWVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3nJbm1w9gixiwasx9TxNYH2K6TA%3D%2F413x761%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPN7MWKDFPNCVFD3T4YX6UDPWVI.jpg&h=bd6aa49c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「安心出行」App要求用家交出大量手機使用權限。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用戶不能查閱過往行蹤<br />\n<br />\n記者下載並開啟程式，介面選項包括「進入」、「上車」和「報告確診或初步確診」，下方有收件箱，用作接收由當局發出的感染風險通知，程式未有讓用戶查看過往到訪紀錄的功能。掃描二維碼後，程式會顯示場所地點，離開時需要選擇「我現在離開」或「我已經離開了」，後者要求再輸入離開時間。<br />\n<br />\n對於Android版本要求用家交出大量手機使用權限，資訊科技界選委、數據科學家黃浩華指，目前用戶不能在程式中查閱自己行蹤，但程式卻要求准許讀取用戶儲存空間，「佢睇到你啲嘢但你睇唔到」，做法奇怪。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"4ba5695126b8a4e5e91cbd06ffb5883a517240c0","tid":2289280,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:13:34.000Z","msg":"中共app"},{"pid":"4ddc115ba1928f710a275d05949abb38e569bb68","tid":2289280,"uid":166792,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:14:45.000Z","msg":"差唔多啦 唔意外"},{"pid":"5315bcc25ce26cfc50e17a30a26c1342a03d9227","tid":2289280,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:16:08.000Z","msg":"裝完再uninstall 會唔會都出事？"},{"pid":"0fc8dae11c178b39cd2fdd17395f5ed04806f1c0","tid":2289280,"uid":180401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:16:16.000Z","msg":"Android又贏"},{"pid":"144fc8dd9dc5806f10abf0f5fa84a5369d78962e","tid":2289280,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"唔擔心 實有弱智用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1309f53ecee287e56655fe6a42408297862318","tid":2289280,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5315bcc25ce26cfc50e17a30a26c1342a03d9227","tid":2289280,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:16:08.000Z","msg":"裝完再uninstall 會唔會都出事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:18:44.000Z","msg":"=中出完宣誓守貞操"},{"pid":"2a96c83c65c534a6be16ee7e53639df877da4393","tid":2289280,"uid":9151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"144fc8dd9dc5806f10abf0f5fa84a5369d78962e","tid":2289280,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"唔擔心 實有弱智用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:20:30.000Z","msg":"班弱智都唔慌有咩野會俾人搞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba29b5f4c5cb2fede311ebea9bd23c677696d6af","tid":2289280,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"有朋友尋日問我借部舊android機，話就係用黎裝呢個垃圾app.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}